defaultWe have already referred to the
default overriding need for the right investment, but we also believe that better signage, real time information on traffic flows and other traffic 
defaultmanagement initiatives can make significant differences.
default  Paras 1.16 to 1.20 provide a good summary of the technical advances that will become available in the near future.  All these are extremely welcome in terms of environmental protection and safety, b
defaultut the advantages will be minimized if, as a result of congestion and under-investment by 2040 (as “Action for Roads” points out) almost a quarter of all travel time could be spent 
